\c 59
\s Izono zabantwana bakoIsrayeli
\p
\v 1 Khangela isandla seN\nd kosi\x + 50.2. Nani 11.23.\x*\nd* kasifinyezwanga ukuthi singasindisi, lendlebe yayo kayinzima ukuthi ingezwa.
\v 2 Kodwa iziphambeko zenu\x + 50.1. 64.7.\x* zehlukanisile phakathi kwenu loNkulunkulu wenu, lezono zenu zibusithile ubuso \add bakhe\add* kini, ukuthi angezwa.
\v 3 Ngoba izandla zenu\x + 1.15.\x* zingcoliswe ngegazi\x + Lilo 4.14.\x*, leminwe yenu ngenkohlakalo; indebe zenu zikhulume amanga\x + 59.4,13.\x*, lolimi lwenu lungunguna ububi\x + Jer. 31.12.\x*.
\v 4 Kakho omemeza ngokulunga, njalo kakho olabhela ngeqiniso\x + 66.16. Zaga 29.9. Jer. 2.35. 25.31.\x*; bathemba okuyize\x + 29.21. 40.17.\x*, bakhulume amanga\x + 59.4,13.\x*; bamitha ububi\x + 33.11.\x*\x + Jobe 15.35. Hlab. 7.14.\x*, bazale isiphambeko\x + Jobe 15.35. Hlab. 7.14.\x*.
\v 5 Bachamusela amaqanda enhlangwana, beluke ubulembu besayobe\x + Jobe 8.14,15.\x*; odla okwamaqanda awo uyafa; lelichotshoziweyo\x + Jobe 39.15.\x* liqhamuka lilibululu\x + 30.6. 41.24. Jobe 20.16.\x*.
\v 6 Ubulembu babo\x + Jobe 8.14,15.\x* kabuyikuba yizembatho, njalo kabayikuzembesa ngemisebenzi yabo. Imisebenzi yabo yimisebenzi yobubi, lesenzo sodlakela sisezandleni zabo.
\v 7 Inyawo zabo zigijimela ebubini\x + Zaga 1.16. Zaga 6.17,18.\x*\x + Roma 3.15-17.\x*; baphangisa ukuchitha igazi elingelacala\x + Zaga 1.16. Zaga 6.17,18.\x*; imicabango yabo yimicabango yobubi; ukubhubhisa lokuchitha\x + Roma 3.15-17.\x*\x + 60.18.\x* kusezindleleni zabo.
\v 8 Indlela yokuthula kabayazi\x + Roma 3.15-17.\x*; njalo kakulasahlulelo emikhondweni yabo\x + Hlab. 17.5.\x*; bazenzela izindlela zabo ezimazombazombe\x + Hlab. 125.5. Zaga 2.15.\x*; loba ngubani ohamba kuzo kayikwazi ukuthula.
\s Abantwana bakoIsrayeli bavuma izono zabo
\p
\v 9 Ngakho-ke isahlulelo sikhatshana lathi, lokulunga kakusifinyeleli. Silindela ukukhanya\x + 59.11. Jer. 8.15. 14.19.\x*, kodwa khangela, ubumnyama; \add silind\add*ela ukukhazimula, \add kodwa\add* sihamba emnyameni omkhulu\x + Zaga 4.19.\x*.
\v 10 Siphumputha umduli njengeziphofu\x + Dute. 28.29. Jobe 5.14. Jobe 12.25. 2 Pet. 1.9.\x*, siphumputhe kwangathi ka\add si\add*lamehlo; sikhubeke emini enkulu\x + Dute. 28.29. Jobe 5.14. Jobe 12.25. 2 Pet. 1.9.\x* kwangathi kukusihlwa, \add si\add*sendaweni ezichithekileyo njengabafileyo.
\v 11 Sonke siyabhonga njengamabhere, silile lokulila njengamajuba\x + 38.14.\x*; silindela isahlulelo, kodwa kasikho\x + 59.11. Jer. 8.15. 14.19 .\x*; losindiso, \add kodwa\add* lukhatshana lathi.
\v 12 Ngoba iziphambeko zethu zandile phambi kwakho, lezono zethu zifakaza zimelene lathi; ngoba iziphambeko zethu zilathi, lobubi bethu siyabazi\x + Jobe 12.3.\x*;
\v 13 ukuphambuka, lokuqambela iN\nd kosi\nd* amanga, lokusuka ekulandeleni uNkulunkulu wethu\x + 59.14. 42.17.\x*, ukukhuluma incindezelo lokuhlamuka, ukukhulelwa lokukhuluma\x + Zaga 24.2.\x* amazwi amanga aphuma enhliziyweni\x + Mat. 12.34,35.\x*\x + 59.4,13.\x*.
\v 14 Ngakho isahlulelo sibuyiselwa emuva\x + 59.14. 42.17.\x*, lokulunga kumi khatshana; ngoba iqiniso liyakhubeka esitaladeni, lobuqotho\x + 57.2.\x* kabulakungena.
\v 15 Yebo, iqiniso liyasilela\x + 34.16.\x*, lowehlukana lobubi uzenza impango\x + Hlab. 76.5.\x*. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasi\add ku\add*bona, njalo kwaba kubi emehlweni ayo ukuthi kakulasahlulelo.
\v 16 Yasibona ukuthi kwakungelamuntu\x + 63.5. Hez. 22.30.\x*, yamangala kakhulu\x + Hlab. 143.4. Mark. 6.6.\x* ukuthi kwakungelamlamuli\x + 53.12. Jer. 15.11. 36.25. Jobe 36.32.\x*; ngakho\x + 63.5. Jobe 40.14.\x* ingalo\x + 40.10.\x* yayo yaletha usindiso kuye, lokulunga kwayo khona kwamsekela\x + 63.5. Hez. 22.30.\x*.
\v 17 Ngoba yembatha ukulunga\x + 61.10. Jobe 29.14.\x* njengebhatshi lensimbi, lengowane yosindiso ekhanda layo; yembatha izembatho zempindiselo\x + 61.2.\x* \add njenge\add*sembatho, yazembesa ukutshiseka njengejazi\x + 61.10. Jobe 29.14.\x*.
\v 18 Njengokwezenzo\x + 63.7.\x*, ngokunjalo izaphindisela\x + Dute. 7.10. Dute. 32.35.\x*, ulaka kwabamelana layo\x + 63.3,5,6. 66.15.\x*, umvuzo ezitheni zayo; ezihlengeni\x + 41.1.\x* uzabuyisela umvuzo.
\v 19 Ngokunjalo bazalesaba ibizo leN\nd kosi\x + Hlab. 113.3.\x*\nd* kusukela entshonalanga, lodumo lwayo kusukela lapho okuphuma khona ilanga. Lapho isitha sizangena njengomfula\x + 17.12,13. Isam. 12.15.\x*, uMoya weN\nd kosi\nd* uzaphakamisa isiboniso\x + 10.18.\x* esimelenev laso.
